I"5<p>At last week’s <a href="http://egu2017.eu/">EGU general assembly</a> members of the <a href="https://o2r.info">o2r</a> and <a href="https://reprozip.org/">ReproZip</a> projects organized the short course <a href="http://meetingorganizer.copernicus.org/EGU2017/session/25726"><em>“Reproducible computational research in the publication cycle”</em></a>. This post is a recap of the course by <a href="http://danielnuest.de/">Daniel Nüst</a>, <a href="https://vickysteeves.com/">Vicky Steeves</a>, and <a href="https://remirampin.com/">Rémi Rampin</a>.</p>
